txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.

Wanted: Squishy goo from the insects and spiders found in the Shire. Bounders are looking for proof of those who are assisting them in keeping the Shire safe. Deliver the items to Hal Hornblower at Hobbiton centre.
'Oh dear. I guess... I guess I should thank you.\n\n'Thank you, kindly.'
'There cannot be any possible use for goo, but the Bounders have still asked me to collect it for them, and so I do.'
Hal Hornblower wants squishy goo. Hal can be found near the stable in the centre of Hobbiton.
Deliver the squishy goo to Hal Hornblower in Hobbiton
You have accepted a task to acquire squishy goo for the Bounders of the Shire. They have deputized Hal Hornblower to collect the items near the stables in Hobbiton.
Wanted: Squishy goo from the insects and spiders found in the Shire. Bounders are looking for proof of those who are assisting them in keeping the Shire safe.
